title: Age Of Empires II: HD Edition v5.8 [DiGiTALZONE]
description:
Age Of Empires II: HD Edition v5.8 [DiGiTALZONE]

In Age of Empires II: HD Edition, fans of the original game and new players alike will fall in love with the classic Age of Empires II experience. Explore all the original single player campaigns from both Age of Kings and The Conquerors expansion, choose from 18 civilizations spanning over a thousand years of history, and head online to challenge other Steam players in your quest for world domination throughout the ages. Originally developed by Ensemble Studios and re-imagined in high definition by Hidden Path Entertainment, and Skybox Labs, Microsoft Studios is proud to bring Age of Empires II: HD Edition to Steam! 

Use Launcher.exe to start the game without mods (faster startup).
Use AoK HD.exe to if you want to use mods.
Use EmuConfig.exe to change your nickname and game language.

DLC Included:

- The Forgotten
- The African Kingdoms
- Rise Of The Rajas

Features:

- Release 07.09.2018
- Original content with latest updates
- Intro movies removed
- Base game in English, additional languages available as a separate Language Pack
- Removed unnecessary clutter left by developer
- Clean install with no unneeded files
- Compatible with mods
- Ready for LAN play

Technical:

- Game build version: 5.8.1 (5.8.30622356)
- Goldberg Steam Emu version: 0.1.0

Additional languages:

- German
- French
- Italian
- Korean
- Spanish
- Simplified Chinese
- Russian
- Japanese
- Dutch
- Portuguese-Brazil
